---
title: Korean Sriracha Beef & Veggies with Rapid Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: This sizzling Korean-style beef is a joy unparalleled. Simplicity is the winner here, with a sriracha stir-fry sauce on the beef strips
being the crowning glory on this quick and easy weeknight winner.

